<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/170183-i-have-one-question-having-just-started">I have one question (having just started the book and reached the part where Richard and Bunny are having cocktails/lunch): WHAT DOES RICHARD LOOK LIKE? I haven&#39;t read a description of Richard yet and can&#39;t picture him in my mind. Thanks.</a>
</div>
